  <lyrics>[V1]
 Diosníy, may jatunmin atiyniyki,
 Diosníy, Qannejilata kawsani.
 /Tukuy sach'aj laqhesnimpis kuyukunku
 Jatun atiyniykiwan./
 
[V2]
 Diosníy, may jatunmin atiyniyki,
 Diosníy, atípasqayku Qanwan;
 /Supaytapis, mundotapis, aychatapis
 Jatun atiyniykiwan./
 
</lyrics></song>